author: danj
msg: Updated these interfaces to reflect changes between WSRMD 2004 draft and WSRMD CD 01. Also added
two new interfaces to represent the new "metadata resource" concept that is present in CD 01; one
is the capability that exposes and EPR to the metadata resource,  the other is for the metadata

author: danj
msg: Changed get/setCapability to throw UnsupportedOperationException, because users shouldn't be trying
to assign properties to capabilities if they have no schema/open content on their WS-resource state
